[I] Secure and fast microVMs for serverless computing

[T] Firecracker is an virtualization technology that is purpose-built for
[T] creating and managing secure, multi-tenant container and function-based
[T] services that provide serverless operational models.

[U] https://firecracker-microvm.github.io/

[A] Firecracker Developers
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/emulator
[F] CROSS

[E] add libseccomp

[L] APL
[V] 1.15.0

[D] 519ed041e020835add435747ff40eb5b3993886bae5b897b1378af8d firecracker-1.15.0.tar.gz https://github.com/firecracker-microvm/firecracker/archive/v1.15.0/

cargoinstopt=
atstage cross && hook_add postmake 5 "cp -vf build/cargo_target/${arch_target}/*/{firecracker,snapshot-editor} $root$bindir"
atstage native && hook_add postmake 5 "cp -vf build/cargo_target/*/{firecracker,snapshot-editor} $root$bindir"
